PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of BETTY MacNEIL, of St. Peter's, Nova Scotia, as a director of Marine Atlantic Inc. to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective December 19, 1998, in the place of Michael B. Murphy, whose term will expire.
